{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a <strong>documentary game</strong> that delves into the history of beliefs in devils and <strong>witches</strong>, layering it with contemporary insights. Immerse yourself in the darkness of the Middle Ages at your own pace, and let <i>Lucifer </i>be your guide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1066740/extras/pasek_DEVILS.png?t=1728898300\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The experience is centered on <strong>story and atmosphere</strong>. You will not find difficult choices, action sequences, or inventory management here; movement is limited to progressing through locations along with the plot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1066740/extras/pasek_WITCHES.png?t=1728898300\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the intricate beliefs surrounding <strong>black magic</strong> from diverse perspectives across time and place. Unravel centuries-old occult knowledge, tracing the evolution of <i>fear </i>and fascination across cultures. Immerse yourself in a rich tapestry of historical and geographical contexts, each offering unique insights into the enigmatic world of dark arts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1066740/extras/pasek_PRIESTS.png?t=1728898300\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a suspenseful story that sheds light on the severe aftermath of blasphemy and the deep fear of <strong>divine consequences</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1066740/extras/pasek_NUNS.png?t=1728898300\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If